{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>You are a beginner magician!</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a beginner magician seeking to graduate from the Arcania magic academy, and to do so you must embark on a wonderful adventure to the ancient crypt to return the golden scroll and graduate as a professional magician! But be careful in the crypt there are challenges that you must solve with a lot of creativity and with your powers to achieve it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479650/extras/Splash_Image.png?t=1739056350\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Extract, cast and combine your powers!</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a beginner magician you will be able to extract elements from the environment and then be able to cast them and interact with the environment. You will also be able to combine these elements to create new powers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479650/extras/CombineElements.gif?t=1739056350\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Solve puzzles in a variety of ways!</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ancient crypt is full of challenges at all levels that can be solved in different ways, will you be able to solve all the mysteries with your creativity?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479650/extras/Resolve.gif?t=1739056350\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the Academy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3479650/fe4e343cb8140058f0d0192046fc356cd0e1ef1d.jpg"},{"name":"Luminous cats","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3479650/e8f76b490bb02be9c400b72c461108d815be8a4e.jpg"},{"name":"Flying knowledge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/